{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"instancetype","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"cameraLookingAtCenterCoordinate:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"centerCoordinate","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"acrossDistance:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@CLLocationDistance","text":"CLLocationDistance","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"distance","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"pitch:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@CGFloat","text":"CGFloat","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"pitch","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"heading:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CLLocationDirection","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@CLLocationDirection"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"heading"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"centerCoordinate","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The geographic coordinate on which the map should be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"centered.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"distance","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The straight-line distance from the viewpoint to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapCamera\/centerCoordinate","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]},{"name":"pitch","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The viewing angle of the camera, measur